	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Moralia/Love_Stories*.html#2
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
(Plutarch, <I>Morals</I>, p772)</A>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note3" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Sertorius*.html#ref3
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">3</A>
<I>Violet</I> and <I>Myrrh.</I>


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note4" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Sertorius*.html#ref4
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">4</A>
<SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">Nursia</SPAN>, in Latin writers, and in Amyot.

	<DIV CLASS="mynote">
	<P CLASS="b0 a0">
Thayer's Note: <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">Nursia</SPAN>, one of the most important cities of the Sabines, is now the very <SPAN CLASS="whole">beauti</SPAN>&shy;ful town of Norcia, my favorite place in Umbria. For a developing site on the town, with comprehensive links to those of other people, see
	<A HREF="
E/Gazetteer/Places/Europe/Italy/Umbria/Perugia/Norcia/Norcia/home.html
	"TARGET="comune"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,Town1,WIDTH,235)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
this orientation page</A>.
	</DIV>


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note5" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Sertorius*.html#ref5
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">5</A>
In 105 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN>


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note6" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Sertorius*.html#ref6
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">6</A>
In 102 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN>


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note7" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Plutarch/Lives/Sertorius*.html#ref7
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">7</A>
In 97 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN> Didius was then <SPAN CLASS="whole">pro-consul</SPAN>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note8" HREF="
